overview:
The Laptop Shoppe, a specialist Dell laptop repair service provider located in Chennai, offers professional Dell laptop repair and support solutions. We provide reliable technical support to businesses and home users throughout the Tamilnadu.We offer the best competitive rates and quick turnaround time for the services that we provide.

Our team of experienced component level technicians have years of combined experience in troubleshooting and fixing various laptop issues of the entire Dell notebook range. We work with all laptop and notebook models of the Dell series that includes Adamo, Studio XPS, Alien ware, Precision Mobile Workstation, Vostro, Inspiron, Studio, XPS and Latitude models.
